<h1><span class="large">The Hybrid Hypothesis</span></h1>
<h2><i>A new theory of human origins</i></h2>
<div class="ff" style="margin:0 0 10px 0">EUGENE M. MCCARTHY, PHD GENETICS, ΦΒΚ</div>
<div class="hornavbar">
    <div class="arrowbox"><a title="Previous page" style="font-size:200%;text-decoration:none" href="http://www.macroevolution.net/human-origins.html">&lt;</a></div>
&nbsp;
