<div class="spacer"></div>
    <div class="spacer"></div>
    <div class="hornavbut"><a title="An alternative theory of evolution" href="http://www.macroevolution.net/table-of-contents.html">Theory</a></div>
    <div class="spacer"></div>
    <div class="hornavbut"><a title="List of works cited" href="http://www.macroevolution.net/hybrid-hypothesis-works-cited.html">Works Cited</a></div>
